title: 111. American Dreams And Reality
itunes:title: 111. American Dreams And Reality
description:
We are not living up to the American values set forth by the founding fathers of our great country. On today's episode, Andy and the crew talk about how your success can inspire people, why everybody identifying as a victim in America takes away from the actual victims and how the truth behind the Coronavirus pandemic will open up people's eyes to the mainstream media's narrative.

  • Get my raw & uncensored advice about success & life delivered to you daily!
